_components._string: Nu bn l tn  ca ti xu - minigame hot nht trn Cng game thu ht hng nghn ngi tham gia th chc chn  s khng th b qua game CHN L. Mt ta game th v khng km cnh ra mt ngi chi vi li chi n gin, d chi d thng. Tuy nhin ngi chi cn c s tnh ton hp l v a ra nhng phn on chnh sc  mang li nhng kt qu nh mong i.
